text: louhdl pel del anakneasar teanglay asasangkhum daoy puokke ban kitthea puokke pitchea trauv ban ke bdeseth . (pel noh) chomnuoy robsa yeung kaban mokadl puokke haey yeung nung sangkroh anaknea del yeung mean chetnea . haey tondakamm robsa yeung nung min trauv ban ke banhchiesa pi krom del br pru td ampeuaeakrak noh laey
